51:01.125 --> 51:02.916
[distant gunfire]

51:02.916 --> 51:04.250
[gasps]

51:08.250 --> 51:10.250
♪ ♪

51:13.166 --> 51:15.041
[groans]

51:15.041 --> 51:16.291
Lucy.

51:23.250 --> 51:24.541
Lucy.

51:27.833 --> 51:29.416
[distant explosions]

51:32.375 --> 51:34.375
[grunting]

51:40.291 --> 51:41.458
Lucy.

51:56.500 --> 51:58.708
[Moldaver] Rose.

52:07.708 --> 52:09.250
[door closes]

52:17.291 --> 52:19.166
[ominous music playing]

52:33.083 --> 52:36.083
[Moldaver breathing heavily]

52:51.958 --> 52:54.583
We did it, Rose.

53:16.375 --> 53:18.416
♪ ♪

53:34.875 --> 53:38.833
What do you suppose your Brotherhood
would do with infinite power?

53:44.041 --> 53:48.208
Maybe you can stop them. Maybe you can't.

53:51.041 --> 53:53.291
Maybe all you can do is try.

